## Event Naming

| Framework | Event Handler |
|-----------|---------------|
| Vanilla | \`addEventListener('ifxClick')\` |
| React | \`onIfxClick\` |
| Angular | \`(ifxClick)\` |
| Vue | \`@ifxClick\` |

## Theming

